Civil engineers John Howard and co have been very busy preparing the trailer park and driving piles into the ground for the fixed access bridge.The foundations for the terminals different buildings are well underway.The aim for the DIFT's port management(DPM)is to take management of the ground as soon as possible.Everthing that is coming into the DIFT area is either on schedule or ahead of schedule.Because of this the DIFT project should be ready on the date they expect it to be ready.
